<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><note n="279-1">The beginning is lost.</note>nivēdyāmuna kicce <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yī dharmmuvu yevvarēni
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁ jeṟicinavāru mahāpātakamusēsina<unclear>vā</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kommiseṭṭi tama tallitaṁḍriki dharmmārttamu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>gā nādiṁḍla vāyābyāmunadikkuna ce<unclear>ṟu</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vu paccima śrīsōmēsvaramahādēvaraku
<lb n="6"/>nivēdyāmunaku nicce <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīni nevvarēniṁ jeṟi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>cinavāru mahāpātakamu sēsinavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="8"/>śrīmattu bejāvāḍasāsanulaina teliki
<lb n="9" break="no"/>vēvurusēsina samayamu yālu caccina [Ā]
<lb n="10"/>yālikiṁgalaṭṭi pāṭitoḍavu maganida
<lb n="11"/>kāni yālivāru penaṁgirē<unclear>ni</unclear> mahāpāta
<lb n="12" break="no"/>kamu sēsinavāru<unclear>ṁ</unclear> koṁḍiseṭi tama talli ta
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁḍripōti seṭṭiki dhammārttaṁ nādi<unclear>ṁ</unclear>ḍla bhō<unclear>yī</unclear>
<lb n="14" break="no"/>svaraśrīmahādēvaraku yakaṁḍavarttidī
<lb n="15" break="no"/>paṁbuna kiccina goṟiyalu 55 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēko
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ni prōlyabōyu naḍapaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nāme
<lb n="17"/>yācaṁdrārkkamu nitya māneṁḍu neyi vō
<lb n="18" break="no"/>yaṁgalavāṁḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmanumahāmaṁḍalēsva
<lb n="19" break="no"/><unclear>ra kulō</unclear>ttuṁgarājēṁdracōḍarājula kiṣṭabhri
<lb n="20" break="no"/>tyuṁḍunu <unclear>gi</unclear>ripaścimakulavārddhivarddhana
<lb n="21" break="no"/><unclear>su</unclear>dhākaruṁḍu<note n="279-2">The rest of the stone is</note>
</p>

